1. Manually sort questions and maintain a DB of questions.
   Three collections:
   - easy
   - medium
   - hard
   
2. Group challenges are created by the server.
3. Group challenges are tagged by the server as easy/medium/hard
4. User can check the currently running challenge based on the level, and also can see how many people are playing so far
5. User can join a groupchallenge as a Guest or as a Logged-In user.
   With Guest login, scores will not be persistent.
6. User gets a practise test before joining the GroupChallenge
7. User can check the scoreboard and find it's own rank and overall statistics.
